name: javax.xml.stream.util.StreamReaderDelegate
comment: This is the base class for deriving an XMLStreamReader filter This class is designed to sit between an XMLStreamReader and an application's XMLStreamReader. By default each method does nothing but call the corresponding method on the parent interface.
